{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-14505/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-14505"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:45:05"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["plan américain"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["high"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, tracking"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["backlighting"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man searches a crowded dance hall from an upper balcony."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14505/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-14505","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14505/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-14505"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14505/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14505/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14505/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14505/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14505/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14505/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14505/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14505/canvas/1/5c492b30-9122-46ec-8cf4-ce0101f219eb","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-02T20:13:13.929Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>This dreamlike scene is intentionally shot and scored to be disorienting, as if viewers are part of the chaos and revelry. Reynolds stands on the balcony as if watching a performance or a screen before him.&nbsp; His layer of the shot is largely stationary, while the characters and props in the background seem to float across the frame in various directions. Likewise, Jonny Greenwood’s melancholy score is overlayed atop the diegetic performance of “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW184417243 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W_6Vs8pADrQ\"><u>Auld Lang Syne</u></a>” by the band onstage and the noise of crowd.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14505/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:41.42764729299351,37.7403463375796,296.2798566878981,198.44247611464957"}}}]}]}]}